Class GwCommand

java.lang.Object
  com.google.calendar.interoperability.connectorplugin.base.messages.GwCommand
Direct Known Subclasses:
AdminCommand, AppointmentCommand, MailCommand, NoteCommand, PassThroughCommand, PhoneCommand, SearchCommand, TaskCommand, UnknownCommand
public abstract class GwCommand
extends Object

Base class for commands coming into the GroupWise connector. Every command should contain at least the name of the header-file it was parsed from and the body of the file (in case someone needs it for additional parsing or logging)
